Third-party FIGlet fonts
    The Figlet renderer (Simtabi\Laranail\Console\Tools\Support\Figlet) parses
    standard FIGlet ".flf" fonts. This package does NOT bundle any third-party
    ".flf" fonts. If you add one, keep its own license/credit alongside it —
    classic FIGlet fonts ship under the FIGlet fonts license or the author's own
    terms.
